<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢١٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٤٠٩ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَهَى عُمَرُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْعَزِيزِ أَنْ يُحْمَلَ الْخَيْلَ إِلَى أَرْضِ الْهِنْدِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>